name: THE CANNABIS SAINT Debut Crypto Beat Tape by GLASSY MUSIC
description: GLASSY MUSIC presents his debut in celebration for 4/20: THE CANNABIS SAINT CRYPTO BEAT TAPE. The cover art of this body of audio works is an extension of THE CRYPTO SAINTS a digital painting series created by GLASS. Each of the CRYPTO SAINTS comes with a soundtrack. ...now THE CANNABIS SAINT presents a whole beat tape consisting of 13 original GLASSY productions.
